          "COMMENT": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                "no evaluation is presented. however the authors give",
                "the following comments,",
                " 1) the previous evaluation bnwl-1685(ref.5) shows much",
                " higher values below 100kev.",
                " 2) the least square fit reported in bnwl-1685 is not",
                " recommended for use due to the inclusion of a",
                " resonance near 2 MeV.",
                " 3) more thin-target experiments are required.",
                " measurements at energies down to 20kev would be of",
                " great value in determining the extrapolation of cross-",
                " section to very low energies.",
                " 4) experiment on t(t,2n) should be performed together",
                " with D(t,n) reaction, because for confirmation of",
                " older T(d,n) measurement.",
                "*following measurements have been checked.",
                "the references are summarized in ''rel-ref'' with other",
                "evaluation works.",
                " -----------------------------------------------------",
                " author(s)  *refe-*   method    * ang-range  * t-energy",
                "            *rence*             * lab.       * MeV,lab",
                " -----------------------------------------------------",
                " Agnew+     *  1  * n,long count*  0         * 0.4-2.22",
                "            *     * n,long count*  0 - 120   * 1.316",
                " Jarmie+    *  2  * a,mag.spec. * 30         *0.95-2.10",
                "            *     * a,mag.spec. * 30 - 120   * 1.9",
                " Govorov+   *  3  * n,mn bath   * total sig. *0.06-1.14",
                "Strel'nikov+*  4  * n,long count*  0         *0.04-0.20",
                " -----------------------------------------------------"
              ]
            }
